quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  11,98,"Yaqdumu qawmahu yawma alqiyamatifaawradahumu annara wabi/sa alwirdu almawrood"
  11,99,"WaotbiAAoo fee hathihi laAAnatanwayawma alqiyamati bi/sa arrifdu almarfood"
  11,100,"Thalika min anba-i alquranaqussuhu AAalayka minha qa-imun wahaseed"
  11,101,"Wama thalamnahumwalakin thalamoo anfusahum famaaghnat AAanhum alihatuhumu allatee yadAAoona min dooni Allahimin shay-in lamma jaa amru rabbika wama zadoohumghayra tatbeeb"
  11,102,"Wakathalika akhthu rabbika ithaakhatha alqura wahiya thalimatuninna akhthahu aleemun shadeed"
  11,103,"Inna fee thalika laayatanliman khafa AAathaba al-akhirati thalikayawmun majmooAAun lahu annasu wathalikayawmun mashhoodun"
  11,104,"Wama nu-akhkhiruhu illali-ajalin maAAdood"
  11,105,"Yawma ya/ti la takallamu nafsun illabi-ithnihi faminhum shaqiyyun wasaAAeed"
  11,106,"Faamma allatheena shaqoofafee annari lahum feeha zafeerun washaheeq"
  11,107,"Khalideena feeha ma damatiassamawatu wal-ardu illama shaa rabbuka inna rabbaka faAAAAalun limayureed"
  11,108,"Waamma allatheena suAAidoofafee aljannati khalideena feeha ma damatiassamawatu wal-ardu illama shaa rabbuka AAataan ghayra majthooth"
